data.description: Looking for newer construction close to the beach, back gate of NAS, and top rated Hellen Caro Elementary? You've found it! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is waiting for its new owner. Perdido Key is an easy 10 minute drive and downtown Pensacola is an easy 25 minutes.  This home boasts architectural roof shingles, Fabric Shield hurricane shutters, rocker residential light switches, bullnose corners, 5 ¼ inch baseboards, and a low maintenance yard. Fenced back yard with covered patio and open deck is perfect for entertaining. This is a must see!
